         <abstract id="aspace_641b233a2bd2d31107554aa88fc28428">Correspondence, minutes, financial records, charters and official acts, inventories of books and other property, and other papers documenting the founding and early history of Yale College. Documents include the original charter of the Collegiate School; letters by and to the first trustees of the school; and the 1718 inventory of books donated to the school by Elihu Yale.</abstract>
    
      </did>
